Our competitive edge lies in our people, structure, and discipline.
We strive to deploy capital in areas where it is temporarily scarce.
We seek to achieve superior risk-adjusted returns through fundamental analysis that emphasizes capital preservation.
Established a quarter century ago, Farallon is a pioneer in the global multi-strategy, value driven approach.



Welcome to Farallon Capital Management


Farallon Capital Management, L.L.C.® is a global institutional asset management firm founded in 1986. Farallon manages equity capital for institutions, including college endowments, charitable foundations and pension plans, and for high net worth individuals.  Read More »



